<div class="rte">
  <div class="main-text wrapper text-center header" id="top">
    <h2>PRIVATE CONCIERGE</h2>
    <hr/>
    <p>
      As a complimentary service to all Blue Light Resort guests, a Private Concierge will personally meet you at your property to ensure a smooth and stress free check-in experience. A quick review of the estate amenities, including how to use features like the hot tub, home entertainment system and gas fireplaces, will ensure you make the most of your lodging and your vacation. Our year-round corporate passes will be at your estate when you arrive. Arrange for groceries to be brought and stocked prior to your arrival. We can recommend and reserve the perfect restaurant or activity for a night on the town.
    </p>
    <p>
      From linens to lift tickets, your Private Concierge is available to assist you with every need.
    </p>
    <p>Let us show you what stress-free vacationing is all about.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid--full services-grid clearfix">
    <h2 class="grid__item">OUR SERVICES</h2>
    <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third airport-nav">
