        <figcaption>
          <h3>AIRPORT SERVICES</h3>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item airport-content">
      <p class="service-content">
        If you need transportation to or from the airport just let us know. We will be happy to arrange your ride.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third grocery-nav">
      <figure class="service-img">
        {{ "service-groceries.png" | asset_url | img_tag }}
        <figcaption>
          <h3>GROCERY SHOPPING</h3>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item grocery-content">
      <p class="service-content">
        Concierge is available to assist you with your every need. Let us arrange for groceries to be bought and stocked prior to your arrival.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third babysitting-nav nav-active">
      <figure class="service-img">
        {{ "service-babysitting.png" | asset_url | img_tag }}
        <figcaption>
          <h3>BABYSITTING</h3>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item babysitting-content">
      <p class="service-content">
        At your request we will supply a highchair, buster seat, pack-n-play. The baby-sitting services we recommend are <a href="//guardianangelbaby.com">Guardian Angel</a> or <a href="//babysittersregistry.com">Babysitters Registry</a>
