  <div class="grid--full recommendations-grid clearfix">
    <h2 class="grid__item">WHAT WE RECOMMEND</h2>
    <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third dining-nav">
      <figure class="recommendation-img">
        {{ "recommend-dining.png" | asset_url | img_tag }}
        <figcaption>
          <h3>FINE DINING</h3>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item dining-content">
      <div class="recommendation-content">
        <section>
          <h3>Foundry Grill</h3>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Awarded Best Brunch by City Weekly Magazine and Best of State for
            American Cuisine. Get an incredible view of 12,000-foot Mount Timpanogos through the wall of windows in the Foundry Grill while you enjoy true Western cooking prepared on the restaurant's large wood-burning grill and rotisserie. In warm weather, the patio opens fo outside dining. The Foundry Grill serves breakfast, lunch and dinner six days a week and brunch and dinner on Sunday.
          </p>
          <p>
            <b>Hours:</b><br>
            Breakfast Monday - Saturday from 7:00 am - 10:30 am<br>
            Brunch Sunday from 9:00 am - 2:00 pm<br>
            Lunch Monday - Saturday from 11:00 am - 4:00 pm<br>
            Dinner Sunday - Thursday from 5:00 pm - 9:00 pm; Friday - Saturday from 5:00 pm - 10:00 pm<br>
            Closed daily 4:00 pm - 5:00 pm
          </p>
          <p><strong>Hours are subject to seasonal changes.</strong></p>
          <p>Reservations are strongly recommended. For more information call (801) 223-4420</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h3>Tree Room</h3>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Recipient of the prestigious AAA Four-Diamond award and the Wine Spectator award. The Tree Room serves seasonal mountain cuisine. The atmosphere is romantic with candlelight and soft illumination accenting the Native American art from Robert Redford's private collection. Casual attire is welcome.
          </p>
          <p>
            <b>Hours:</b><br>
            Tuesday - Thursday from 5:00 pm - 9:00 pm<br>
            Friday - Saturday fro 5:00 pm - 10:00 pm
          </p>
          <p><strong>Hours are subject to seasonal changes.</strong></p>
          <p>Reservations are strongly recommended. For more information call (801) 225-4107</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h3>Deli</h3>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Enjoy the deli's fresh sandwiches, pastries, and other desserts while sitting on the deck outside or up on the mountainside. Handcrafted foods from American cottage farmers as well as items produced right at Sundance are also available.
          </p>
          <p>
            <b>Hours:</b><br>
            Sunday - Thursday from 7:00 am - 9:00 pm<br>
            Friday - Saturday from 7:00 am - 10:00 pm
          </p>
          <p><strong>Hours are subject to seasonal changes.</strong></p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h3>Creekside Caf&eacute;</h3>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Creekside offers a fast alternative for a Sundance dining experience. Located just above Sundance Mountain Outfitters, Creekside's menu consists of pizza, salad, chili, pastries, soup, coffee and hot chocolate. Enjoy the warms inside or the view of Mt. Timpanogos on the patio.
          </p>
          <p>
            <b>Hours:</b><br>
            8:00 am - 4:00 pm
          </p>
          <p><strong>Hours are subject to seasonal changes.</strong></p>
          <p>During the winter months, Creekside provides Skier's Fast Food, and a Saturday BBQ.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third spa-nav">
      <figure class="recommendation-img">
        {{ "recommend-spa.png" | asset_url | img_tag }}
        <figcaption>
          <h3>SPA SERVICES</h3>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item spa-content">
      <p class="recommendation-content text-center">
        The Spa at Sundance offers complete spa packages for your mind, body and spirit. Let us make a reservation for you or visit the <a href="//sundanceresort.com/spa-en.html">Sundance Resort website</a> for more information.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third ski-nav nav-active">
      <figure class="recommendation-img">
        {{ "recommend-ski.png" | asset_url | img_tag }}
        <figcaption>
          <h3>SKI GEAR &amp; RENTALS</h3>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item ski-content">
      <p class="recommendation-content text-center">
        You can rent your skis and equipment from Sundance or make a short stop at <a href="//www.nymans-ski-shop.com">Nyman's Ski Shop</a> just before you head up the canyon, with 25 years experience on the slopes without having a worry about equipment issues. We suggest you try on your equipment so you can get that perfect fit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="back-to-top"><a href="#top">BACK TO TOP</a></p>
</div>

<script>
  jQuery(function($) {
    $(document).ready(function(){
      function navToggle (navEls, contentEls, category) {
        $(navEls).removeClass('nav-active');

        $(contentEls).hide();

        $('.'+category+'-nav').addClass('nav-active');
        $('.'+category+'-content').show();
      }

      var serviceToggle = navToggle.bind(null, '.airport-nav, .grocery-nav, .babysitting-nav', '.airport-content, .grocery-content, .babysitting-content');

      $('.airport-nav').click(serviceToggle.bind(null, 'airport'));
      $('.grocery-nav').click(serviceToggle.bind(null, 'grocery'));
      $('.babysitting-nav').click(serviceToggle.bind(null, 'babysitting'));

      var recommendToggle = navToggle.bind(null, '.dining-nav, .spa-nav, .ski-nav', '.dining-content, .spa-content, .ski-content')

      $('.dining-nav').click(recommendToggle.bind(null, 'dining'));
      $('.spa-nav').click(recommendToggle.bind(null, 'spa'));
      $('.ski-nav').click(recommendToggle.bind(null, 'ski'));
    });
  });
</script>
